{"tid":545630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"身處呢個速食世代，好驚比人背叛","createTime":"2018-01-30T16:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T19:56:12.000Z","uid":59670,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9d982ac2292c88841cf4c7cd9a6583bf2d9459","tid":545630,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"對上一次拍拖好傷，失戀嗰陣個心好似撕裂左咁...<br />\n依家時隔兩年，依然放低唔到，個心好似穿左個lone 永遠都修補唔返咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同現任一齊左幾個月，佢知我既過去所以好努力咁比安全感我，我亦都感受到佢好愛我<br />\n<br />\n但我真係好驚所有野都會有完既一日，我無辦法再承受同樣既傷害，比信任既人背叛同欺騙既感覺傷到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我係咁同自己講 唔好咁上心 要保持距離 做好隨時抽離既準備 有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb498812a154b4d5d1472984f2f2878e921c9ae8","tid":545630,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老"},{"pid":"ae5d502ab1652a692a3902845cda1ce1fe681922","tid":545630,"uid":12360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"既然佢都相信你 比到信心你<br />\n點解唔試下相信佢 比d信心佢？"},{"pid":"38a613de840eee6d088d0917dd02fe90a7e1ed71","tid":545630,"uid":89840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:03:20.000Z","msg":"留意到樓主經常發埋好多負能量post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3149dd16fdb4eb6c3607b939c33b499df94459c","tid":545630,"uid":136143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔可以太愛一個人"},{"pid":"403967d4d5155a231779579e9088997a23b4b266","tid":545630,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T19:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9961adc8e0d239bddb6c42c14f5cadc3039906a","tid":545630,"uid":27993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco